ation between large, similar masses, low spin\nand low eccentricity will help to accelerate the searches for\ngravitational-wave signals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Dec 2015 18:59:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 Dec 2015 19:37:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 29 Feb 2016 13:45:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-23"}
