ich have a common \"canon\"\ndiscussed among all books in the area, as shown by high topic overlap and low\nalignment distance even in small sample sizes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Dec 2015 23:07:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Feb 2016 21:12:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 13 Feb 2017 15:48:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-14"}
